content:
This build was released on the 14th of August, 2021.
This build contains general bugfixes.
There are no differences between the Mario and Luigi versions of this build.

New areas:
Course 8 Area 6: Scary Sewer Maze (warped)
Course 8 Area 7: Scary Sewer Maze (warped) [again?]
Secret 3 Area 4: [some JRB-type level]
